69.label: Get ready to update call post contact

0.name: Data
Comments
0.value:
Add custom form data to call

We will keep contact open for 5 minutes after last update - or until agent is no-longer in ACW

Note we now also allow a 'post' call update - this shows data in the interactions page

We use the CXone token - this script is not portable and must be updated for all BU

0.name: Data
0.value:
//Allow us to add to interactions/search

DYNAMIC CustomUserFields

CustomUserFields.CallerName = "{global:aatcrn1}"
CustomUserFields.CallerSchool = "{global:aatcrn2}"
CustomUserFields.CallerRole = "{global:aatcrn3}"
CustomUserFields.CallerQuery = "{global:aatcrn4}"
CustomUserFields.ActionTaken = "{global:aatcrn6}"

IF "{global:aatcrn5}" = "Yes"
	{	CustomUserFields.CallerFollowUp = "true" }
ELSE
	{	CustomUserFields.CallerFollowUp = "false"}



global:callDetails = "AgentName:{global:First} {global:Last}|CallDateTime:{now}|CallerNumber:{global:ANI}|Skill:{global:sklname}|CallerName:{CustomUserFields.CallerName}|CallerSchool:{CustomUserFields.CallerSchool}|CallerRole:{CustomUserFields.CallerRole}|CallerQuery:{CustomUserFields.CallerQuery}|CallerFollowUp:{CustomUserFields.CallerFollowUp}|ActionTaken:{CustomUserFields.ActionTaken}"
global:callDetails.savetodb(1)
